          " 20 for not qualifying (includes 10 points for attending and 10 for not qualifying but making at least one qualifying pass) </br>
          " 40 for qualifying (round one loser) (plus qualifying points and any bonus points)</br>
          " 60 for semi finish (round two loser) (plus qualifying points and any bonus points)</br>
          " 90 for r/u (plus qualifying points and any bonus points)</br>
          " 120 winner (plus qualifying points and any possible bonus points)</br>
